description:
Alexa can help you control your Frigidaire Cool Connect Smart Air Conditioners.

Try saying ...

- Alexa, turn on the air conditioner.
- Alexa, lower the air conditioner by 2 degrees.
- Alexa, set the air conditioner to 68 degrees.

Login using the same credentials you use in the Frigidaire mobile application.

To ensure a consistent experience, please set your temperature unit preferences to be the same within the Alexa and Frigidaire applications.
For help, please contact us at SmartHelp.US@frigidaire.com
name: Frigidaire
shortDescription: Control your Frigidaire Cool Connect Smart Air Conditioner.
